  "2026-06-04T16:17:24.205Z",maintainer-agent,"Shipped: pm close-many. Routes EACH matched item through full runClose semantics (ensureCloseReason, active-child orphan checks, blocked-edge cleanup, validate-close) — unlike update-many --status closed which bypasses them. Requires >=1 filter (never matches all) + shared --reason. Skips already-terminal unless --force. --dry-run previews per-item plan (close/skip + active_child_ids). Checkpoint+rollback via new shared core/checkpoint/mutation-checkpoint.ts (also refactored update-many onto it, DRY, passes 24-line duplicate-chunk gate). Optional shared --resolution/--expected/--actual. Full wiring + 100%-covered shared modules."
close_reason: Delivered pm close-many with full runClose semantics + dry-run + checkpoint/rollback
